title: Ask Yourself's Vegan Bloodsport: A Failed Paradigm.
description:
"Ask Yourself" is the name of a vegan activist youtube channel, known for a peculiar form of confrontational debate (with both vegans and non-vegans).  You can find his channel, here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQNmHyGAKqzOT_JsVEs4eag/videos 
Meanwhile, à-bas-le-ciel has a playlist of videos criticizing Ask Yourself: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZEkgohG7k7o1jwm5FHUI0Jkh1-14bKce
